    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I see. So it's basically saying if something goes wrong, I might be responsible for costs I didn't even cause? Are there any \"hidden\" ways these clauses can be used against someone, or any specific wording that usually signals a more predatory or aggressive liability stance?",
